text: Silvia Parietti (born 19 March 1978) is a road cyclist from Italy. She represented her nation at the 2001, 2003 and 2004 UCI Road World Championships. In 2005, she won the Italian National Road Race Championships. ==References== ==External links== * Profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1978 births Category:Italian female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
